description: APP_PIS_INSTRUMENT Reference key to instrument
APP_CONTRACT_DT The date on which contract was booked
APP_AMT_FINANCED Total amount financed
APP_CR_LMT Credit limit(Original)
APP_TERM Term of the contract(Original)
APP_DRAW_TERM Number of term draw period is allowed
APP_REPMT_TERM The repayment term of the contract
APP_RATE The contract rate
APP_INDEX_TYPE_CD Reference key to lookup index type such as prime  etc
APP_INDEX_RATE Index rate(Original)
APP_MRATE The margin rate(Original)
APP_BALLOON_AMT Contract balloon payment amount
APP_FIRST_PMT_DT The date on which first payment should be received
APP_MATURITY_DT The date on which the account would mature(Original)
APP_FINANCE_CHARGE The finance charge or total estimated interest charge on the contract
APP_TOTAL_OF_PMTS Total of all payments or total note amount
APP_TOTAL_DOWN_PMT_AMT Total down payment amount of contract
APP_TOTAL_SALE_PRC Total sale price of the asset on contract
APP_PMT_AMT Payment amount(Original)
APP_APR Annual percentage rate
APP_PRM_CODE Reference Key to Promotion Coe
APP_MATURITY_INDEX_TYPE_CD Reference key to lookup index type such as prime  etc
APP_MATURITY_MRATE The maturity margin rate
APP_PCB_BRANCH_CSS Reference key to portfolio branch(Servicing)
APP_COLLECTOR_USR_CODE Collector associated with account
APP_CPP_CODE Reference Key to Compensation plan code
APP_RATE_BUY The buy rate of the contract
APP_COMP_AMT Total Compensation amount
APP_FEE_AMT_ESCROWED Total escrow advance amount received (original)
APP_COMP_AMT_UPFRONT Upfront compensation amount
APP_COMP_AMT_REMAINING Remaining compensation amount
APP_RATE_SPREAD Rate spread for HMDA reporting
APP_HOEPA_CD Home ownership and equity protection act code for HMDA reporting
APP_LIEN_STATUS_CD Lien status code for HMDA reporting
APP_COUPON_FIRST_PMT_DT The date on which first payment is expected on the re-ordered coupon book
APP_COUPON_ORDER_BY Identifies coupon ordered by
APP_COUPON_ORDER_DT The date on which coupon book was re-ordered
APP_COUPON_ORDER_IND Indicates whether the coupon has been re-ordered
APP_COUPON_START_NO The starting number of the coupon
APP_EARLY_PRE_PMT_PENALTY_IND Indicates if early repayment fee can be charged
APP_PRE_PMT_TOLERANCE_AMT Tolerance amount to calculate pre-payment penalty fee
APP_PROM_CANCEL_DLQ_DAYS Stores the delinquency days after which the promotion is cancelled automatically
APP_CR_CONSUMED Credit limit already consumed on account
APP_FINAL_PMT_AMT Final payment amount
APP_STAGE_FUND_IND Indicates if stage funding is allowed
APP_COLLECT_INTEREST_IND Indicates whether the interest has to be collected or not
APP_PROM_TOLERANCE_AMT Promotion tolerance amount checked against outstanding balance for promotion benefits
APP_PROM_PERIOD_TYPE_CD Promotion period type
APP_ACH_BANK_NAME The name of the ACH bank of the customer
APP_ACH_BANK_ROUTING_NBR The 9-digit ABA number of the ACH bank of the customer
APP_ACH_ACCOUNT_TYPE_CD Reference key to lookup ACH account type such as checking saving etc
APP_ACH_ACCOUNT_NBR The account number of the bank for ACH transaction
APP_ACH_PMT_DAY The actual day that the ACH payment will be taken out of the customer account
APP_ACH_PMT_AMT Amount of payment used in ACH transaction
APP_ACH_PMT_FREQ_CD Reference key to lookup ACH payment frequency such as weekly monthly etc
APP_ACH_START_DT The date on which ACH processing started
APP_ACH_IND Indicates whether the account has been setup for ACH
APP_RPMT_CUR_CURRENCY_CODE Reference key to Currency  Repayment Currency (Current)
APP_PDC_IND PDC indicator for applications
APP_ORIG_SYS_XREF Reference key to application id of legacy system
APP_PTC_COMPANY Reference key to portfolio company
APP_PCB_BRANCH Reference Key to portfolio branch(Origination)
APP_NBR A unique application number
APP_DT The effective date of the application
APP_PRD_PRODUCT Reference key to product
APP_SOURCE_CD Identifies the source of the application such as Fax  Web
APP_UNDERWRITER_USR_CODE The underwriter who approved the credit application
APP_PRO_TYPE_CD Reference key to lookup producer type such as dealer  agent  etc
APP_PRO_NBR Reference to producer number
ADC_PRP_PRICING Reference Key to Product Pricings
ADC_CR_GRADE_CD The application decision approved credit grade
ADC_CR_SCORE The application decision credit score
APP_TOTAL_DISCOUNT_RATE Stores the Total Discount Rate. This is used for Conversion of data from other system
APP_ORIG_SYS_XREF Reference key to application id of legacy system
APP_PTC_COMPANY Reference key to portfolio company
APP_PCB_BRANCH Reference Key to portfolio branch(Origination)
APP_NBR A unique application number
APP_DT The effective date of the application
APP_PRD_PRODUCT Reference key to product
APP_SOURCE_CD Identifies the source of the application such as Fax  Web
APP_UNDERWRITER_USR_CODE The underwriter who approved the credit application
APP_PRO_TYPE_CD Reference key to lookup producer type such as dealer  agent  etc
APP_PRO_NBR Reference to producer number
APP_CONVERSION_DT Date of conversion
APP_NEW_IND Indicates converting new account
APP_LINK_EXISTING_CUSTOMER_IND Indicates whether the account should be linked to existing customer
APP_MULTIPLE_OFFER_IND Indicates if Multiple offer is enabled for the branch. This is used for Conversion of data from other system
APP_REPMT_FIXED_PRINCIPAL_AMT Stores the Repayment Principal Amount. This is used for Conversion of data from other system
APP_EXTEND_BALLOON_TERM_MAX Stores the Maximum Extended Balloon Term. This is used for Conversion of data from other system
APP_TIME_ZONE_CD Stores the Time Zone Code. This is used for Conversion of data from other system
APP_STMT_PREFERENCE_MODE_CD Application Statement Preference Mode code
APP_CLASS_TYPE_CD Application class type code (SBL/INV/BUS)
APP_LINKED_ACC_NBR Indicates the linked account number for an account
APP_MULTI_BILL_ASSET_RATE_IND Indicates whether multiple asset rates are applicable for one billing period or not
APP_PAH_HIERARCHY_CODE Payment Hierarchy Code
APP_PMT_MODE_CD Reference lookup to Accounts payment mode current (cash/check)
APP_STMT_PREFERENCE_MODE_CD Application Statement Preference Mode code
APP_RATE_MAX_INCREASE_YEAR Maximum allowable increase in rate in a year
APP_ACCRUAL_CALC_METHOD_CD Reference key to lookup accrual calculation method such as actuarial  sum of digits or simple interest
APP_RATE_MAX_INCREASE_LIFE Maximum allowable increase in rate in the life of the contract
APP_TOTAL_OF_PMTS_ESTIMATED Application Total Of Payments Estimated
CREATED_BY Standard Who
CREATION_DATE Standard Who
APP_ACH_FEE_IND Application ACH fee indicator
APP_ADV_DRAW_END_DT The end date to draw advance for stage funded loans
APP_AGREEMENT_TYPE_CD Agreement type Code - Usage/Rental/Undefined.
APP_API_ID Unique Sequence number for multi threading
APP_CAP_COST_GRO Application Capital Cost Gross
APP_CAP_COST_RED Application Capital Cost Residual
APP_CHARGE_CALC_METHOD_CD Charge caluclation method code for Tiered / Non Tiered.
APP_COMP_REVISE_PLAN_TERM Compensation plan revision term
APP_CONTRACT_VERIFY_BY Contract Verify Date
APP_COUPON_NOS Number of coupons for order
APP_DISCOUNT_AMT Discount Amount applicable for Rental Billing
APP_DISCOUNT_PER Discount Percentage
APP_DRAW_TERM_RATE Stores the rate at the time of stage funding
APP_ERROR_IND Indicates error on conversion record
APP_EXCESS_RENT_COL_METHOD_CD Excess rent colculation method code for Actual/Average.
APP_FLEXIBLE_REPAYMENT_IND Indicates flexible repayment schedule is allowed or not
APP_INDEX_RATE_EFFECTIVE Stores the Index Effective rate
APP_INSTALLMENT_METHOD_CD Method to calculate payment amount Equated EQ Final Payment Differs FPD
APP_MASTER_ACC_IND Indicates if the application is marked as master account or not
APP_MASTER_ACC_NBR Master account number to which the application is linked
APP_MATURITY_MRATE_EFFECTIVE Stores the effective maturity margin rate
APP_MAX_TIME_BAR_YEAR Staging data source : Max Time Bar Year
APP_MAX_USAGE Maximum units allowed per cycle.
APP_MRATE_EFFECTIVE Stores the Effective for the margin
APP_PMT_MAX_INCREASE_LIFE Application Payment max increase life
APP_PMT_MAX_INCREASE_YEAR Application Payment max increase year
APP_PREPAID_AMT Application Prepaid Amount
APP_PROBABLE_DELIVERY_DT Application probable delivery date
APP_PROFIT_RATE Application profit rate
APP_PROM_PROFIT_RATE Application promotional profit rate
APP_RATE_BUY_EFFECTIVE Stores the effective buy rate
APP_RATE_CHG_FREQ_TYPE_CD Reference key to lookup rate change frequency type such as MONTHLY QUARTERLY etc
APP_RATE_CHG_PERIOD Stores the time or period between subsequent rate change based on rate adjustment frequency
APP_RATE_CHG_RSC_METHOD_CD Reference key to lookup Rate Change Reschedule Method
APP_RATE_CHG_RSC_VALUE The percentage value to be used to change the payment amount when rate changes on account
APP_RATE_EFFECTIVE Stores the Effective rate
APP_RECOURSE_TYPE_CD Stores Recourse Type from lookup code
APP_RENTAL_FEE Application Rental fee
APP_RENT_END_DATE Rental End Date
APP_RENT_FACTOR Application Rent Factror
APP_RENT_START_DATE Rental Start date with timestamp
APP_RENT_VAL Application Rent Value
APP_REPAYMENT_SKIP_PERIOD Stores all months that are allowed to skip payment such as MARCH APRIL MAY
APP_REPAYMENT_TYPE_CD Reference key to lookup account repayment type
APP_REQ_BALLOON_AMT Application Requested Balloon amount
APP_RESIDUAL_DAYS Application residual days
APP_RESIDUAL_PER Application  Residual Percentage
APP_RESIDUAL_VAL Application Residual Value
APP_SALES_TAX_AMT_ESTIMATED Application Sales Tax Amount Estimated
APP_SALES_TAX_PER_ESTIMATED Application Sales Tax Percentage Estimated
APP_SECURITY_DEPOSIT_AMT Application Security Deposit Amount
APP_SIGNING_DT Application signing date
APP_STMT_CONSOLIDATE_IND Application statement consolidation indicator
